Enum ModemStatusEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ModemStatusEvent>
      • com.digi.xbee.api.models.ModemStatusEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ModemStatusEvent>

    public enum ModemStatusEvent
extends Enum<ModemStatusEvent>
    Enumerates the different modem status events. This enumeration list is intended to be used within the ModemStatusPacket packet.
